Hand #5, team1 (-2), zeteswithhugedec (2)
team1 posts the blind of 1
zeteswithhugedec posts the blind of 2
Dealt to team1 [3s 6s 6c]
Dealt to zeteswithhugedec [8c Th Ts]
team1 raises to 24
zeteswithhugedec calls
*** FLOP *** (48) [2c 8s 7s]
zeteswithhugedec bets 3
team1 raises to 59
zeteswithhugedec calls
zeteswithhugedec discards [8c]
team1 discards [3s]
*** TURN *** (166) [2c 8s 7s] [8h]
zeteswithhugedec bets 12
team1 raises to 204
zeteswithhugedec calls
*** RIVER *** (574) [2c 8s 7s 8h] [Kc]
zeteswithhugedec bets 53
team1 raises to 113
zeteswithhugedec folds
Uncalled bet of 60 returned to team1
team1 wins the pot (680)




